title: The Arms Race in the NFL | GM Street (Ep. 290)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss Aaron Rodgers's new deal, Teddy Bridgewater's new team, Kirk Cousins's role in setting the QB market, and 'Hard Knocks.'
